svn
^^^
	+ Disabled the options for removing shared files when uninstalling a
	  package, both in porg and grop. Now shared files are never removed,
	  as it ougth to be.
	+ Disabled support for missing files.
	+ Removed command line option alias --owner
	+ grop: Removed support for gzip/bzip and stripping of libraries.
	+ grop: Replaced menu option "Unselect all" by the more standard 
	  "Invert selection" on the files popup menu.

2.0.9
^^^^^
	+ Fixed minor bug in GPorg.


